Package: lms
Title: Lab Manual Style (UCD-SERG lintr Configuration)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("UCD-SERG", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "serg@ucdavis.edu")
Description: Shared lintr linter configuration implementing the UCD-SERG
    lab manual style guide. Applied repositories consume this via a thin
    '.lintr.R' that calls lms::default_linters() and supplies their own
    local exclusions.
